==English==
===Adjective===
'''nonlinear'''
#(''of a set of points'') not lying on a [[straight line]]
#{{chemistry}} (''of a molecule'') whose [[atom]]s do not lie in a straight line
#{{mathematics}} (''of an equation'') having an [[exponent]] not equal to one
#(''of a system'') whose [[output]] is not [[linearly]] [[dependent]] on its [[input]]
# [[erratic]] and [[unpredictable]]

